<--CREATE A NUMBER GUESSING GAME-->

REQUIREMENTS
1)  Algorithm should choose a number from 1-10 randomly.
2)  User should have 3 chances to guess the right number.
3)  If User guesses the right number then the points scored should increase. After 3 wrong guesses the game ends.

FURTHER IMPORVEMENTS
1)  User should choose the level of difficulty (Easy, Moderate, Hard), accordingly the range of numbers should increase.
2)  Except in the difficulty level Easy, the code should supply hints to the user after each wrong guess. 
    The hints could be saying that the number to be guessed is a multiple of another number, or providing a upper limit and lower limit of that number.
